{"tid":2250244,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"斥保育者阻發展 揚言打餐大","createTime":"2020-10-20T03:36:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-20T05:53:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c6cef28dc15a2c5cec79e95dfa266ce525733954","tid":2250244,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T03:36:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201020/CFUJMJC64BA4HMWXR7A34WCRMQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201020%2FCFUJMJC64BA4HMWXR7A34WCRMQ%2F&d=h9s%2FmsO%2BhBO0acKdDJaYES9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=09d4501e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201020%2FCFUJMJC64BA4HMWXR7A34WCRMQ%2F&h=e68d5628\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201020/CFUJMJC64BA4HMWXR7A34WCRMQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n斥保育者阻發展 揚言打餐大<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JEI1pds1VG4f6D77AQ7__y8mW6Q=/1769x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/L4YZGRPAZBHKLMDN6GBIEMFOVI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJEI1pds1VG4f6D77AQ7__y8mW6Q%3D%2F1769x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FL4YZGRPAZBHKLMDN6GBIEMFOVI.jpg&h=8afd44c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■早前有指中央會撥出珠海桂山島予香港發展。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】歷時五個月的「土地大辯論」未有全面支持發展明日大嶼，但特首林鄭月娥仍不心息，豪言要「打餐大」，一次過開拓近兩千公頃土地，又斥保育人士與政府對抗而拖慢覓地進度。環團反駁指保育是全球趨勢，甚至連內地亦禁止填海，反指林鄭才是小眾。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：疑討地失敗 硬推明日大嶼  林鄭歪論「習搞保育 港要填海」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n朱凱廸轟無知不識大勢<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥接受傳媒訪問時提到，發展明日大嶼比起「插針樓」好，建插針樓只是「短暫止痛藥」，形容既然每次覓地「次次打餐死，不如打餐大，一次過開拓一、兩千公頃土地」。她希望明日大嶼繼九龍東後成為本港第三個商業區，否則「如何有整幢寫字樓，讓其掛上公司名」。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭又大嘆造地問題辛苦，稱土地開發工作較1997年「起碼艱難十倍八倍」。她歸。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n綠色和平資深項目主任連佩怡對林鄭言論表示驚訝，她反駁環境保育議題乃全球趨勢，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n面對林鄭批評，連認為林鄭才是社會少眾，批評她未有按土地大辯論報告建議，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n立法會前議員朱凱廸亦斥林鄭稱保育意識高漲拖慢造地的說法，只顯出其無知，。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"dc023e317509208ad0b51036ef6f7041e4825ba5","tid":2250244,"uid":121146,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T03:43:31.000Z","msg":"直接過戶比支共算啦  扮乜鳩"},{"pid":"deeeac2be8fc6d9f41b71dc9edadc6b06612c928","tid":2250244,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T03:45:00.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">甚至連內地亦禁止填海，反指林鄭才是小眾。</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8fc4f2f5ee7d1ed9bf66bf3ac25ac8a932cec8f","tid":2250244,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T03:45:56.000Z","msg":"乜撚野叫打餐大<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b78d59af368fd681573a3172d86c2a48f278c0d7","tid":2250244,"uid":330227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T04:52:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n高爾夫球場 新界棕地"},{"pid":"3aed7db9b3a18f84329e4b0483ea6a12e0e6df15","tid":2250244,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T04:53:38.000Z","msg":"解放軍來了"},{"pid":"274bbc35841a3c6709a91f732e17458bd79cecd9","tid":2250244,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T04:54:30.000Z","msg":"高分低能真係有樣睇"},{"pid":"db1248fd767d9d90c1abc95a66e33aa75ca7e267","tid":2250244,"uid":271545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T05:15:35.000Z","msg":"★林鄭：習近平重視保育，填海幾乎是